        <h1>From Adversarial Scarcity to Relational Sovereignty</h1>
        <p class="hero-sub">
          We are designing ethically-governed, AI-assisted mediation ecosystems that de-escalate conflict, protect children from systemic trauma, and transform family resolution from a win–lose tribunal into a shared architecture of healing.
        </p>
        <div class="hero-actions">
